    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fivehtihs laid irr tas wiſſinaugſtakajs STIPRAIS DEEWS / kas tawus Genaid- neekus tawa Rohka nodewis irr/ unn wiꞥſch dewe tam tohs Defmi- tus no wiſſahm Leetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehniſch no So- domas fazzija us Ahbramui: Dohd man tohs Laudis / un to Mantu reemn preeffch tewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams fazzija us to Kehniſu no Sodomas : Es eſmu farwi Rohkn pazehtis us to KUN- GU to wiſſinaugſtakn STIP- RU DEEWU / kam Debbes unn Semme peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja es kahdi Pawedeni/ jeb weenn Kurpes-Sikfni / jeb (zittu ko) xenifchu no wiſſeem/ kas tew peederr / ka tu ne warri faazziht : Es eſmu Ahbramui bag- gatu darrijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ween to/ ko tee Jan- nekti irr apehdnfchi/ unn to Wihro Daltu / kas ar man gahjnfchi/ Ahnera/ Eſkola unn Mamrea/ lat tee neimn farwi Daltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ehz Schahin Leetahim tikke ta KUNG Wahrdz us Ahbr weena Parahdiſchanā/tazzid Es eſmu teiw par Preekſcht mahm Bruhnahm/ unn taw ga irr tohti leela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ahbra Kungs / KUNGS / ko tu dohti / unn es eemn ta bes neem/ unn mans Nainma u ga Dehis irr fchis Damafke Eliēsers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams fazzija : gi/man ne effi tu Dsimmum wis / unn redſi mannas Sa Behrns buhs mans Mantn\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un raugi / ta KUNG Wahrdz notieke uhs wiannu/ zidans : Schis ne buhs Mantneeks/ bet kas no tan Mecfahm nahks/ tas buhs Mantas-Mehnejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch iswedde to unn fazzija : Luhko jelle us De unn fkaiti tahs Swaigſnes/w tu tahs fkaitibt? Un wiꞥſch ja us to: ta patt buhs taws mums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch tizzeja eef KUNGU / unn tas peelahg wiẍam to par Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija us wi Es eſmu tas KUNGS / ka tew isweddis eſmu no Ur ta deëru/ ka es tew fcho Semni tu eemantcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Ku KUNGS / pee ka noprat es/ ka es to eemantofchu?\n"
    }
  ],
